    JAVASCRIPT INTERACTIVITY

    Include essential JavaScript for interactivity:

    html
    <script>
// Accordion functionality
const accordions = document.getElementsByClassName("accordion");
for (let i = 0; i < accordions.length; i++) {
    accordions[i].addEventListener("click", function() {
        this.classList.toggle("active");
        const panel = this.nextElementSibling;
        if (panel.style.maxHeight) {
            panel.style.maxHeight = null;
        } else {
            panel.style.maxHeight = panel.scrollHeight + "px";
        }
    });
}

// Progress tracking
function updateProgress() {
    const checkboxes = document.querySelectorAll('.mastery-checklist input[type="checkbox"]');
    const checked = document.querySelectorAll('.mastery-checklist input[type="checkbox"]:checked');
    const percentage = (checked.length / checkboxes.length) * 100;
    document.querySelector('.progress-fill').style.width = percentage + '%';
}

// Search functionality
function searchFunction() {
    const input = document.getElementById('searchBox');
    const filter = input.value.toUpperCase();
    const sections = document.getElementsByTagName('section');
    
    for (let i = 0; i < sections.length; i++) {
        const txtValue = sections[i].textContent || sections[i].innerText;
        if (txtValue.toUpperCase().indexOf(filter) > -1) {
            sections[i].style.display = "";
        } else {
            sections[i].style.display = "none";
        }
    }
}

// Quiz answer checking
function checkAnswer(questionNumber) {
    const selected = document.querySelector(`input[name="q${questionNumber}"]:checked`);
    const feedback = document.getElementById(`feedback${questionNumber}`);
    
    if (selected) {
        // Add answer checking logic
        feedback.innerHTML = '<p class="correct"> Correct! [Explanation]</p>';
    } else {
        feedback.innerHTML = '<p class="warning">Please select an answer</p>';
    }
}

// Time tracking for study sessions
let startTime = Date.now();
window.addEventListener('beforeunload', function() {
    const studyTime = Math.round((Date.now() - startTime) / 60000);
    localStorage.setItem('lastStudyTime', studyTime);
});

// Print-friendly version
function printNotes() {
    window.print();
}
</script>
